***<br />\nlink就識放喇，字就唔撚睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上reddit睇左喇<br />\n佢support ps4係3.5mm only<br />\n唔係usb<br />\n換言之usb聽到聲用唔到咪<br />\n<br />\n師兄<br />\n你睇清支援ps4<br />\n都有分3.5mm同埋usb架"},{"pid":"f64e647942beeea4def5b344ce5bccd7d7643e41","tid":378975,"uid":100283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我cloud I 再可直插PS4</blockquote><br />\n師兄cloud I有usb頭嗎？</blockquote><br />\n有. Usb頭直插ps4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyperxgaming.com/tw/headsets/cloud-gaming-headset\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyperxgaming.com%2Ftw%2Fheadsets%2Fcloud-gaming-headset&d=fvQSApAbqDN5XdEmsHtYApUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=92398a2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyperxgaming.com/tw/headsets/cloud-gaming-headset</a><br />\n<br />\n師兄Are you sure?</blockquote><br />\n相容於 PC、 Xbox One&reg;*、 Xbox One S*、 PS4&trade;、 PS4 Pro、 Mac&reg;、 行動裝置** and VR***<br />\nlink就識放喇，字就唔撚睇</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我cloud I 再可直插PS4</blockquote><br />\n師兄cloud I有usb頭嗎？</blockquote><br />\n有. Usb頭直插ps4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyperxgaming.com/tw/headsets/cloud-gaming-headset\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyperxgaming.com%2Ftw%2Fheadsets%2Fcloud-gaming-headset&d=fvQSApAbqDN5XdEmsHtYApUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=92398a2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyperxgaming.com/tw/headsets/cloud-gaming-headset</a><br />\n<br />\n師兄Are you sure?</blockquote><br />\n相容於 PC、 Xbox One&reg;*、 Xbox One S*、 PS4&trade;、 PS4 Pro、 Mac&reg;、 行動裝置** and VR***<br />\nlink就識放喇，字就唔撚睇</blockquote><br />\n但係Cloud I好似真係無得usb插ps4。佢唔似Cloud II咁跟張usb sound card，你quote個段相容於XXX應該係指3.5mm頭（插手制）。至於Cloud I如果另外買個usb sound card得唔得我就唔清楚。"},{"pid":"baf8b87156fb7220e0e6f5847efc60cc14eaea07","tid":378975,"uid":114856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T